        donec est. Odio penatibus risus viverra tellus varius sit neque erat
        velit.
      </p>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
        <img
          src={jjLookingOut}
          alt="jj at the beach looking out"
          class="rounded-xl shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-white/10"
          width="2432"
          height="1442"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">
          I'll figure out what to put here eventually
        </h2>
